{"name":"Adding 1, 2, 3","bg":"/img/story/bg/classroom.png","age":0,"translations":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Сложение на 1, 2, 3"}],"items":[{"name":"Now let’s learn how to add 1, 2, and 3.","actor":"Teacher","dialogType":"Normal","translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Теперь давай научимся прибавлять 1, 2 и 3."}],"actions":[]},{"name":"Okay! What does that mean?","actor":"Student","dialogType":"Normal","translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Хорошо! А что это значит?"}],"actions":[]},{"name":"It means we start with a number and move forward. Like steps \uD83D\uDC63.","actor":"Teacher","dialogType":"Normal","translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Это значит, что мы начинаем с числа и делаем шаги вперёд. Как шаги \uD83D\uDC63."}],"actions":[]},{"name":"Let’s try 4 \u002B 1. Start at 4 and take one step. What’s next?","actor":"Teacher","dialogType":"Normal","translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Попробуем 4 \u002B 1. Начни с 4 и сделай один шаг. Что дальше?"}],"actions":[]},{"name":"Five!","actor":"Student","dialogType":"Normal","translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Пять!"}],"actions":[]},{"name":"Exactly! Now 6 \u002B 2. Start at 6 and take two steps.","actor":"Teacher","dialogType":"Normal","translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Точно! А теперь 6 \u002B 2. Начни с 6 и сделай два шага."}],"actions":[]},{"name":"Seven, eight! It’s 8!","actor":"Student","dialogType":"Normal","translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Семь, восемь! Получается 8!"}],"actions":[]},{"name":"Great! And now 5 \u002B 3?","actor":"Teacher","dialogType":"Normal","translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Молодец! А теперь 5 \u002B 3?"}],"actions":[]},{"name":"Six, seven, eight! The answer is 8!","actor":"Student","dialogType":"Normal","translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Шесть, семь, восемь! Ответ — 8!"}],"actions":[]},{"name":"Let’s try one more! What is 7 \u002B 2?","actor":"Teacher","dialogType":"Normal","translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Попробуем ещё один! Сколько будет 7 \u002B 2?"}],"actions":[{"name":"9","isCorrect":true,"score":1,"translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"9"}]},{"name":"8","isCorrect":false,"score":0,"translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"8"}]},{"name":"10","isCorrect":false,"score":0,"translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"10"}]}]},{"name":"Well done! You’re getting faster at counting!","actor":"Teacher","dialogType":"Normal","translates":[{"lang":"ru-RU","name":"Отличная работа! Ты всё быстрее считаешь!"}],"actions":[]}],"actors":[{"id":"Teacher","name":"Teacher","image":"/img/story/npc/npc_teacher.png","s":"f"},{"id":"Student","name":"Student","image":"/img/story/npc/npc_student.png","s":"u"}]}